    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a reliable daily driver without the brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it's ready to hit the road for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you'd like to take it for a spin or have any questions at all!",
