    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains composed via updated bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the model's signature 50/50 weight distribution. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and rod bearing inspections\u2014are well-documented. A visceral, analog machine optimized for technical driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained mechanicals. Clean interior. Ready for immediate sale.",
