      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. It's in great shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a spontaneous weekend getaway! Everything runs smoothly, the interior is nice and clean, and it's totally ready for its next adventure. I've really loved having this car, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
