    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, and the braking system provides consistent bite with no fade. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a pure analog connection to the road. A meticulously maintained specimen of BMW's finest engineering era.",
